claim.claim-text:
A control system for a solar power conversion unit configured to convert direct-current power output by at least one solar cell (20) into alternating-current power, the control system comprising:
a power detecting section (41, 42) configured to detect the power output by the solar cell (20);
an insolation amount inputting section (46) to which an index related to an amount of insolation is input;
a power correcting section (47) configured to correct the output power detected by the power detecting section (41, 42) on the basis of the index related to the amount of insolation input to the insolation amount inputting section (46); and
a voltage controlling section (45) configured to change an output voltage of the solar cell (20) on the basis of the output power corrected by the power correcting section (47) such that the output power of the solar cell (20) approaches a maximum power point.
